The '''Belnar Sector Force''' was a military organization in the [[Belnar/Legends|Belnar]] [[Star system/Legends|system]].

==History==
They were direct enemies to an opposing military group in the system, the [[Peltsic League]]. At some point before [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]], the Belnar Sector Force was led by [[Khil]] master tactician, [[Tarlo Ganar]]. Thanks to Ganar, the Sector Force eventually defeated the League.<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

